1. Use click package to manage CLI.
2. Define option for reading the HTML parsing the metadata to JSON.
3. Define option for writing the metadata from JSON to the photos.


Some examples

> fbfix read -f /path/to/file.html -o /path/to/file.json
Reads the single file.html and outputs metadata to file.json

> fbfix read -d /path/to/html_dir/ -o /path/to/file.json
Reads all html files in directory and outputs metadata to file.json

> fbfix write /path/to/file.json -d /path/to/photo_dir/
Applies provided metadata in file.json as EXIF to photos in photo_dir
